I also want to learn about the qualities that go into a relationship, such as compromise, and learn more about myself as a person.
hardestPartOfDating: The hardest part about dating is finding people who want to date me and whom I also want to date. I am very adaptive, but I can not adapt if I can't find the things I am looking for: maturity and depth.
